## Key Features Implemented

### Backend
- **Auth**: JWT access (15m) + refresh (7d httpOnly cookie) with bcrypt (12 rounds)
- **Permissions**: Pure helper functions (`canAccessBatch`, `canSendMessage`, `canModerate`, `canAdmin`, `canEscalate`)
- **REST API**: All routes per spec — batches, members, messages, mod-queue, notifications, subscriptions, admin, mentor
- **Socket.IO**: Real-time messaging, typing indicators, @mention notifications, personal rooms
- **Validation**: Zod schemas on all inputs
- **Error Handling**: AppError class, Prisma/Zod error mapping, global handler
- **Rate Limiting**: Redis-backed 100 req/min per IP (graceful fallback)
- **File Upload**: Multer with mime whitelist, local `/uploads` folder
- **Admin Logging**: Automatic in service layer via `logAdminAction()`

### Frontend
- **Slack-like Layout**: Three-column (sidebar, chat, member panel)
- **Zustand Stores**: auth, batch, message, notification, ui — with persist middleware
- **React Query**: All REST calls with auto-cache invalidation
- **Socket Hook**: `useSocket()` with all event handlers and emit helpers
- **Role-Based UI**: Guest banners, locked batches, admin badge, mentor dashboard
- **Dark Theme**: Glassmorphism, gradients, smooth transitions throughout
